arStrings.szText: "Is there anything I can do to help?"
Ah... well, yes. There is. There is a sacred Zakarum relic within our tombs. I have learned of a thief who wishes to add it to their collection.
Deciding if he could ask you for such a thing.

The relic is a symbol, you see, used to properly lay our dead to rest. It represents the Light that shines eternal within all of us. It is a beacon of hope for all. It uh... forgive me. It is quite important.
Rambling. His passion is overwhelming his restraint. Returning to stoicism at the end.
If you could return the holy symbol, we would be in your debt. Not only for keeping it out of the hands of a thief, but also for bringing some comfort to our sick here.
